## ROLE/PERMISSION SYSTEM (source of truth: src/lib/permissions.ts)

| Role | Display | Access |
|------|---------|--------|
| `free` | Free Plan | [N] seats, core features only |
| `pro` | Pro Plan | Unlimited seats, all features |
| `admin` | Admin | Full access + billing management |

Never hardcode role strings inline. Always use the permissions helper.

