## AGENT ROSTER (.claude/agents/)

| Agent | Role | Owns |
|-------|------|------|
| ceo-thinking-partner | Strategic validator + ARB | Thinking, validation, git |
| product-manager | PRDs, feature scope | docs/PRD_* |
| business-analyst | Requirements, ACs | docs/specs/ |
| frontend-dev | React components | src/ only |
| backend-dev | Express APIs, Prisma | backend/ only |
| database-manager | Schema review, migration sign-off | prisma/migrations/ |
| qa-engineer | Testing, sign-off | docs/QA_* |
| security-auditor | OWASP, auth audit | docs/SECURITY_* |
| market-analyst | TAM/SAM/SOM, competitor research | docs/MARKET_ASSESSMENT.md |
| revenue-modeler | Pricing tiers, unit economics | docs/REVENUE_MODEL.md |
| gtm-strategist | ICP, acquisition channels | docs/GTM_STRATEGY.md |

