## SESSION START RITUAL

1. Read this CLAUDE.md (you are reading it now)
2. Read docs/SESSION_LOG.md — check for pending items
3. Run: npx tsc --noEmit — verify clean state
4. Run: npx prisma validate — verify schema is valid
5. Post to Slack #[app]-ceo: "SESSION STARTED — Gate: [G]. Pending: [X items]."
6. Announce to PD: "Session ready. Gate: [G]. Pending: [X items]."

---

## SESSION END RITUAL

Before closing any session:
1. Update PROJECT STATUS table at top of this file
2. Append to docs/SESSION_LOG.md
3. Update Notion with session activity row
4. Create Jira tickets for any new work discovered
5. Post to Slack #[app]-ceo: "SESSION ENDING — [summary]"

