## SLACK CHANNEL REGISTRY

Workspace: [your-org].slack.com

**Posting method:** `node scripts/slack-post.cjs <CHANNEL> "<message>"`

| Channel | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| #[app]-ceo | Orchestration, commits, deploys, session open/close |
| #[app]-alerts | Blockers, vetoes, escalations ONLY |
| #[app]-build | Frontend/backend agent actions |
| #[app]-quality | QA and security findings |
| #[app]-business | Research, pricing, GTM |

