## STRIPE INTEGRATION NOTES

**Products:** [List your Stripe product IDs once created, e.g., prod_xxxxxxxx]
**Prices:** [List your Stripe price IDs, e.g., price_xxxxxxxx for monthly, price_xxxxxxxx for annual]
