## DATABASE NOTES

**ORM:** Prisma
**Database:** PostgreSQL (Railway)
**Migration command:** npx prisma migrate deploy
**Schema file:** prisma/schema.prisma

Core tables:
- `users` — Auth0 user ID, email, role, stripe_customer_id
- `subscriptions` — user_id, stripe_subscription_id, status, plan, current_period_end
- `[YOUR_CORE_ENTITY]` — [description of your main business object]

Database agent rule: database-manager must review all schema changes before migration runs.

